Every system ran on the same harness with the same model and budgets, scored by a judge blind-validated against a second judge (90.6% agreement, Cohen's kappa 0.81). Full per-system tables, the code-intelligence result, and reproduction commands: **[BENCHMARKS.md](/Graphify-Labs/graphify/blob/v8/BENCHMARKS.md)**.

